{"tid":491062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【地面打樁出事】深圳地鐵11號線大停駛 服務受阻8粒鐘","createTime":"2017-12-06T07:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T16:48:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff33c9b5a4306505123724d0c8efcf6baa4aefe","tid":491062,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512540257_ad98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512540257_ad98.jpg&h=42550103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512541553_845e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512541553_845e.jpg&h=257585f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳地鐵11號線今晨7時許出現大停電，列車服務大受影響，直至下午2時，服務至今仍未完全恢復。深圳地鐵下午2時許表示，初步預計仍需時5小時才能完成搶修。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，今晨7時許，11號線00503次列車在行駛至紅樹灣南-后海（往碧頭方向）時，因列車無法行駛而執行應急程序，往碧頭方向的列車在前海灣折返。<br />\n<br />\n由於事發時處於上班繁忙時間，受事故影響的沿途車站受擠滿乘客，無數乘客遭遇遲到，加上列車行經寶安機場，亦令民眾未能趕上飛機。<br />\n<br />\n深圳地鐵於官方微博發表公佈，指今晨（12月6日）7時許，外部施工單位（正業建設有限公司）在為業主方（深圳市昂塞特體育用品有限公司）進行項目（昂賽特攀岩基地）工程時，未經審批的情況下擅自進行打樁工程，造成地鐵11號線紅樹灣南-后海區段（往碧頭）方向接觸網設備受損，全線運行受阻，大量乘客滯留。<br />\n<br />\n本次故障由於外單位違規施工，導致11號線接觸網受損、供電中斷，過程中部份部件掉落致一列車車頭受損，事件中無乘客受傷。由於觸網受損較大、維修難度較高，因此，故障排查搶修時間相對較長，預計全面恢復時間將有所延長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171206/57547525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57547525&d=06gfd3pA%2Fau4FvtBh%2FCmGjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=febf04b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57547525&h=ce2a8ef7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171206/57547525</a>"},{"pid":"80c394973785fccf8ea286295fbbbbcd535e42ab","tid":491062,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"超級香港又一例證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8d2a45bac84a3fee57a15ff948d4e0f419aea1","tid":491062,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:21:27.000Z","msg":"屌穿隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b751bab2e4ea55116b708fc68096358f553e89","tid":491062,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"冇爆炸，仲唔多謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6f50fdf6268fac619e28fcba88a22b78d469b9","tid":491062,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"條樁直穿車卡會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee69117df7c36549b5edbf7f8800bb672e98e031","tid":491062,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:47:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超越香港又一例證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0ef7afe88dc308291645d9419a9cfb7befef2a43","tid":491062,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條樁直穿車卡會點<img src=